amendment.description: An amendment numbered 75 printed in Part B of House Report 116-119 to increase funding by $1 million for the NASA Office of Science, Technology, Engineering and Mathematics Engagement, for the purposes of supporting the NASA Space Grant College and Fellowship Program.
